    <title>MarkdownAdvance</title>
    <url>/2020/03/21/MarkdownAdvance/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown-高级功能"><a href="#Markdown-高级功能" class="headerlink" title="Markdown 高级功能"></a>Markdown 高级功能</h1><blockquote>
<p>本篇内容参考了<a href="https://www.runoob.com/markdown/md-advance.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown 高级技巧-菜鸟教程</a>，首先进行感谢。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-符号转义"><a href="#1-符号转义" class="headerlink" title="1.符号转义"></a>1.符号转义</h2><p>Markdown语法通过特殊符号实现，当需要单独显示这些符号时，可在特殊符号前增加转义符号<code>\</code>，同时通过该符号所设置的格式也不会被解析。  </p>
<figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**加粗**</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span>转义<span class="symbol">\*</span><span class="symbol">\*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>加粗</strong><br>**转义**  </p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>Markdown中需要使用转义显示的符号如下：  </p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">Fuhao</th>
<th align="center">type</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">\</td>
<td align="center">反斜线</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">`</td>
<td align="center">反引号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">*</td>
<td align="center">星号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">_</td>
<td align="center">下划线</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">()</td>
<td align="center">小括号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">[]</td>
<td align="center">方括号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">{}</td>
<td align="center">花括号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">#</td>
<td align="center">井号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">+</td>
<td align="center">加号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">-</td>
<td align="center">减号</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">.</td>
<td align="center">小数点</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">!</td>
<td align="center">感叹号</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="2-公式"><a href="#2-公式" class="headerlink" title="2.公式"></a>2.公式</h2><p>在Markdown中插入公式前，需要开启Mathjax公式渲染。</p>
<p><strong>行内公式：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight gams"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">函数：<span class="symbol">$</span>f(x)=ax+b<span class="symbol">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>函数：$f(x)=ax+b$</p>
<p><strong>单行公式：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight gams"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">$</span><span class="symbol">$</span>E=mc^<span class="number">2</span><span class="symbol">$</span><span class="symbol">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">$</span><span class="symbol">$</span>\<span class="built-in">sin</span>(\alpha)^&#123;\theta&#125;=\sum_&#123;i=<span class="number">0</span>&#125;^&#123;n&#125;(x^i + \<span class="built-in">cos</span>(f))<span class="symbol">$</span><span class="symbol">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>$$E=mc^2$$<br>$$\sin(\alpha)^{\theta}=\sum_{i=0}^{n}(x^i + \cos(f))$$</p>
<p><strong>多行公式：</strong><br>使用LaTex格式公式</p>
<figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">f(x) = <span class="symbol">\i</span>nt_&#123;-<span class="symbol">\i</span>nfty&#125;^<span class="symbol">\i</span>nfty</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="symbol">\h</span>at f(<span class="symbol">\x</span>i)<span class="symbol">\,</span>e^&#123;2 <span class="symbol">\p</span>i i <span class="symbol">\x</span>i x&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="symbol">\,</span>d<span class="symbol">\x</span>i</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>$$<br>f(x) = \int_{-\infty}^\infty<br>    \hat f(\xi),e^{2 \pi i \xi x}<br>    ,d\xi<br>$$</p>
<figure class="highlight tex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">mathbf</span><span class="string">&#123;V&#125;</span></span>_1 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">times</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">mathbf</span><span class="string">&#123;V&#125;</span></span>_2 =  <span class="tag">\<span class="name">begin</span><span class="string">&#123;vmatrix&#125;</span></span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">mathbf</span><span class="string">&#123;i&#125;</span></span> &amp; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">mathbf</span><span class="string">&#123;j&#125;</span></span> &amp; <span class="tag">\<span class="name">mathbf</span><span class="string">&#123;k&#125;</span></span> <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial X&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial u&#125;</span></span> &amp;  <span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial Y&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial u&#125;</span></span> &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial X&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial v&#125;</span></span> &amp;  <span class="tag">\<span class="name">frac</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial Y&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;\partial v&#125;</span></span> &amp; 0 <span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula"><span class="tag">\<span class="name">end</span><span class="string">&#123;vmatrix&#125;</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$&#123;$tep1&#125;&#123;<span class="tag">\<span class="name">style</span><span class="string">&#123;visibility:hidden&#125;</span><span class="string">&#123;(x+1)(x+1)&#125;</span></span>&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="formula">$$</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">注：由于Hexo Markdown渲染问题，LaTex换行符<span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span>需要改写成<span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span><span class="tag">\<span class="name">\</span></span>才能被正确识别</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>$$<br>\mathbf{V}_1 \times \mathbf{V}_2 =  \begin{vmatrix}<br>\mathbf{i} &amp; \mathbf{j} &amp; \mathbf{k} \\<br>\frac{\partial X}{\partial u} &amp;  \frac{\partial Y}{\partial u} &amp; 0 \\<br>\frac{\partial X}{\partial v} &amp;  \frac{\partial Y}{\partial v} &amp; 0 \\<br>\end{vmatrix}<br>${$tep1}{\style{visibility:hidden}{(x+1)(x+1)}}<br>$$</p>
<h2 id="3-流程图"><a href="#3-流程图" class="headerlink" title="3.流程图"></a>3.流程图</h2><p>Hexo默认不支持Markdown流程图，需要添加支持：</p>
<figure class="highlight processing"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --<span class="built_in">save</span> hexo-<span class="built_in">filter</span>-flowchart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装完成后，重启<code>hexo server</code>即可启用流程图支持</p>
<figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">``` \flow</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">st</span>=&gt;start: 用户登陆</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">op</span>=&gt;operation: 登陆操作</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">cond</span>=&gt;condition: 登陆成功 <span class="literal">Yes</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> <span class="literal">No</span>?</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">e</span>=&gt;end: 进入后台</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op-&gt;cond</span><br><span class="line">cond(<span class="literal">yes</span>)-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">cond(<span class="literal">no</span>)-&gt;op</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line">注：flow前的\是为了防止代码被解析，使用时须去掉</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<div id="flowchart-0" class="flow-chart"></div>

<p>流程图使用<code>flow</code>语法，可分为两部分，分别定义模块和模块之间的连接。<br><strong>定义模块</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight vim"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">tag</span>=&gt;<span class="built_in">type</span>: conten<span class="variable">t:</span>&gt;url</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>其中<code>tag</code>为模块名，<code>type</code>为模块类型，共有6种：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">Type</th>
<th align="center">说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">start</td>
<td align="center">开始</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">end</td>
<td align="center">结束</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">operation</td>
<td align="center">操作</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">subroutine</td>
<td align="center">子程序</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">condition</td>
<td align="center">条件</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">inputoutput</td>
<td align="center">输入或输出</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p><code>content</code>指框图种显示的文本，注意<code>type:</code>与文本之间须有一个空格。<br><code>url</code>是与文本绑定的链接。  </p>
<p><strong>定义连接</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight xl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">tga1</span>-&gt;</span>tag2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">tag1</span>-&gt;</span><span class="function"><span class="title">tag2</span>-&gt;</span>tag3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">注：连接可两两配对分开定义，也可连续定义</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用<code>-&gt;</code>连接两个模块，对于<code>condition</code>类型，需要分别对两个分支指定连接。</p>
<figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">condition1<span class="function"><span class="params">(<span class="literal">yes</span>)</span>-&gt;</span>tag1</span><br><span class="line">condition1<span class="function"><span class="params">(<span class="literal">no</span>)</span>-&gt;</span>tag2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/raphael/2.2.7/raphael.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flowchart/1.6.5/flowchart.min.js"></script><textarea id="flowchart-0-code" style="display: none">st=>start: 用户登陆
op=>operation: 登陆操作
cond=>condition: 登陆成功 Yes or No?
e=>end: 进入后台

st->op->cond
cond(yes)->e
cond(no)->op</textarea><textarea id="flowchart-0-options" style="display: none">{"scale":1,"line-width":2,"line-length":50,"text-margin":10,"font-size":12}</textarea><script>  var code = document.getElementById("flowchart-0-code").value;  var options = JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(document.getElementById("flowchart-0-options").value));  var diagram = flowchart.parse(code);  diagram.drawSVG("flowchart-0", options);</script>]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Language</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Markdown</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
