    <title>MarkdownHTML</title>
    <url>/2020/03/19/MarkdownHTML/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown-HTML-标签"><a href="#Markdown-HTML-标签" class="headerlink" title="Markdown HTML 标签"></a>Markdown HTML 标签</h1><p>Markdown可以解析HMTL标签，因此可以使用HTML标签实现Markdown基本语法，同时实现一些Markdown不支持的功能</p>
<blockquote>
<p>本篇内容参考了博客文章<a href="https://wuchenxu.com/2015/12/30/Markdown-html-compare/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown语法对应的HTML标签实现-Wu Chenxu</a>，首先进行感谢。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.标题"></a>1.标题</h2><p>使用HTML标签实现多级标题</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span> 标题 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span> 标题 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span> 标题 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1> 标题 </h1>
<h2> 标题 </h2>
<h3> 标题 </h3>

<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="2-格式"><a href="#2-格式" class="headerlink" title="2.格式"></a>2.格式</h2><p>使用HTML标签实现文字格式设置</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span> 斜体 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span> 斜体 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span> 粗体 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span> 粗体 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span> 删除线 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span> 删除线 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span> 下划线 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span> 下划线 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><em> 斜体 </em><br><i> 斜体 </i><br><strong> 粗体 </strong><br><b> 粗体 </b><br><del> 删除线 </del><br><s> 删除线 </s><br><ins> 下划线 </ins><br><u> 下划线 </u>  </p>
<p>利用HTML标签实现上下标</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">H<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span>O</span><br><span class="line">E=mc<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O<br>E=mc<sup>2</sup>  </p>
<p>利用HTML标签设置字体和颜色</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">'4'</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">'blue'</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">'KaiTi'</span>&gt;</span>Hello World<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><font size='4' color='blue' face='KaiTi'>Hello World</font>  </p>
<h2 id="3-引用"><a href="#3-引用" class="headerlink" title="3.引用"></a>3.引用</h2><p>利用HTML标签实现引用嵌套</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span> 引用 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span> 引用 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">blockquote</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span> 引用 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span> 引用 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">q</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote> 引用 <blockquote> 引用 </blockquote></blockquote>  
<q> 引用 <q> 引用 </q></q>  

<h2 id="4-分割线"><a href="#4-分割线" class="headerlink" title="4.分割线"></a>4.分割线</h2><p>利用HTML标签设置分割线</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr />  

<h2 id="5-图片"><a href="#5-图片" class="headerlink" title="5.图片"></a>5.图片</h2><p>利用HTML标签设置图片格式</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png"</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">"QB.png"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"500"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"500"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png" alt="QB.png" width="500" height="500" />  

<p>还可以利用HTML为图片嵌入超链接</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/media/md28220105"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png"</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/bangumi/media/md28220105" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png"> </a>  </p>
<h2 id="6-超链接"><a href="#6-超链接" class="headerlink" title="6.超链接"></a>6.超链接</h2><p>利用HTML标签添加超链接</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.bilibili.com"</span>&gt;</span> BiliBili <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> BiliBili </a>  </p>
<h2 id="7-列表"><a href="#7-列表" class="headerlink" title="7.列表"></a>7.列表</h2><p>利用HTML标签实现列表<br>无序列表</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> Apple <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> Banana <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> Grape <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
  <li> Apple </li>
  <li> Banana </li>
  <li> Grape </li>
</ul>

<p>有序列表</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span> <span class="attr">start</span>=<span class="string">3</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> Why <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> When <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> Where <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol start=3>
  <li> Why </li>
  <li> When </li>
  <li> Where </li>
</ol>  

<h2 id="8-表格"><a href="#8-表格" class="headerlink" title="8.表格"></a>8.表格</h2><p>利用HTML标签实现表格</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span> <span class="attr">border.</span>'<span class="attr">1</span>' <span class="attr">summar</span>=<span class="string">'students\'</span> <span class="attr">list</span>'</span></span><br><span class="line">  &lt;caption&gt; List &lt;/caption&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> Name <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> Age <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span> Grade <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> John <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 12 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 7 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> Mike <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 10 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span> 5 <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<table border.'1' summar="students' list"
  <caption> List </caption>
  <tr>
    <th> Name </th>
    <th> Age </th>
    <th> Grade </th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td> John </td>
    <td> 12 </td>
    <td> 7 </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td> Mike </td>
