    <title>MarkdownTest</title>
    <url>/2020/03/18/MarkdownTest/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Markdown基础语法与测试"><a href="#Markdown基础语法与测试" class="headerlink" title="Markdown基础语法与测试"></a>Markdown基础语法与测试</h1><blockquote>
<p>本篇内容参考了博客文章<a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/191d1e21f7ed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Markdown基本语法-高鸿祥</a>，首先进行感谢。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.标题"></a>1.标题</h2><p>文字前加#设置标题</p>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题</span><br><span class="line">##### ……</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<h1 id="一级标题"><a href="#一级标题" class="headerlink" title="一级标题"></a>一级标题</h1><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id="四级标题"><a href="#四级标题" class="headerlink" title="四级标题"></a>四级标题</h4><h5 id="……"><a href="#……" class="headerlink" title="……"></a>……</h5></blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="2-格式"><a href="#2-格式" class="headerlink" title="2.格式"></a>2.格式</h2><p>文字两边加* \ _ \ ~设置格式</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span>   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗**</span>   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__加粗__</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***斜体加粗**</span>*   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___斜体加粗__</span>_  </span><br><span class="line">~~删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：<br><em>斜体</em><br><em>斜体</em><br><strong>加粗</strong><br><strong>加粗</strong><br><strong><em>斜体加粗</em></strong><br><strong><em>斜体加粗</em></strong><br><del>删除线</del>    </p>
<h2 id="3-引用"><a href="#3-引用" class="headerlink" title="3.引用"></a>3.引用</h2><p>引用文字前加&gt;，可嵌套</p>
<figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>&gt;引用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：   </p>
<blockquote>
<p>引用</p>
<blockquote>
<p>引用</p>
<blockquote>
<p>引用</p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="4-分割线"><a href="#4-分割线" class="headerlink" title="4.分割线"></a>4.分割线</h2><p>三个及以上-或*</p>
<figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">----</span><br><span class="line">**<span class="strong">*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">*</span>***<span class="strong">*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="显示效果如下："><a href="#显示效果如下：" class="headerlink" title="显示效果如下：   "></a>显示效果如下：   </h2><hr>
<hr>
<hr>
<h2 id="5-图片"><a href="#5-图片" class="headerlink" title="5.图片"></a>5.图片</h2><p>语法：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt</span>](<span class="link">url "title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">alt: 图片标签</span><br><span class="line">url: 图片地址，可为超链接或相对路径</span><br><span class="line">title: 图标标题，鼠标指向时显示</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>示例：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">QB.png</span>](<span class="link">https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png "QB"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：<br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png" alt="QB.png" title="QB"></p>
<p>注：Markdown不能指定图片高度与宽度，可使用HTML语言的img标签</p>
<figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;img <span class="attribute">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png"</span> <span class="attribute">width</span>=<span class="string">"50%"</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：<br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/17/OWtxXFTC7SHUbyV.png" width="50%"></p>
<h2 id="6-超链接"><a href="#6-超链接" class="headerlink" title="6.超链接"></a>6.超链接</h2><p>语法：  </p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">content</span>](<span class="link">url "title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">content: 超链接显示文字</span><br><span class="line">url: 超链接</span><br><span class="line">title: (可选)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>示例：  </p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">百度</span>](<span class="link">https://www.baidu.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：<br><a href="https://www.baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a>   </p>
<p>注：Markdown语法不支持新页面打开超链接，可使用HTML语言的a标签代替</p>
<figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a <span class="attribute">href</span>=<span class="string">"url"</span> <span class="attribute">target</span>=<span class="string">"_blank"</span>&gt;content&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>例如： <a href="https://www.baidu.com" target="_blank">百度</a>   </p>
<h2 id="7-列表"><a href="#7-列表" class="headerlink" title="7.列表"></a>7.列表</h2><h3 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h3><p>文字前添加-,+或*表示</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">- </span>列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+ </span>列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">* </span>列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：   </p>
<ul>
<li>列表   </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>列表   </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>列表   </li>
</ul>
<h3 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h3><p>文字前添加序号1.</p>
<figure class="highlight angelscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> 列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2.</span> 列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3.</span> 列表</span><br><span class="line">注：序号与内容之间须有空格</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：   </p>
<ol>
<li>列表  </li>
<li>列表  </li>
<li>列表  </li>
</ol>
<h3 id="列表嵌套"><a href="#列表嵌套" class="headerlink" title="列表嵌套"></a>列表嵌套</h3><p><strong>上一级与下一级之间加三个空格</strong>  </p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1. </span>一级列表  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">	- </span>二级列表  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2. </span>一级列表  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    * </span>二级列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：   </p>
<ol>
<li>一级列表  <ul>
<li>二级列表    </li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>一级列表  <ul>
<li>二级列表    </li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="8-表格"><a href="#8-表格" class="headerlink" title="8.表格"></a>8.表格</h2><p>语法：</p>
<figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title|<span class="string">title</span>|title</span><br><span class="line">---|<span class="string">:-:</span>|<span class="string">---:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">content</span>|<span class="string">content</span>|content</span><br><span class="line">content|<span class="string">content</span>|content</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第二行分割表头与内容，并设置内容格式</span><br><span class="line">- 占位，可多个</span><br><span class="line">内容文字默认居左，:-: 文字居中，--: 文字居右</span><br><span class="line">注：原生语法两端都有|<span class="string">，可省略</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>示例：  </p>
<figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">name |<span class="string"> age </span>|<span class="string"> grade</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">---- </span>|<span class="string"> :-: </span>|<span class="string"> ---:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">John </span>|<span class="string"> 12  </span>|<span class="string"> 7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Mike </span>|<span class="string"> 10  </span>|<span class="string"> 5</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示效果如下：  </p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>name</th>
<th align="center">age</th>
<th align="right">grade</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>John</td>
<td align="center">12</td>
<td align="right">7</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Mike</td>
<td align="center">10</td>
<td align="right">5</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="9-代码"><a href="#9-代码" class="headerlink" title="9.代码"></a>9.代码</h2><p>单行代码以反引号``包含</p>
<figure class="highlight arcade"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">`code;`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>代码块以三个反引号```上下包含</p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>显示效果如下：<br><code>code;</code>  </p>
<figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>也可使用在开头制表符(TAB)或四个空格</p>
<pre><code>function()
{
    return 0;
}</code></pre><hr>
]]></content>
